nsters soon start to hunt them down and as they get closer to the thunderbolt it seems that something more sinister awaits them…</p>  <figure class=\"element element-image element--thumbnail\" data-media-id=\"0a4fdce01e2d68712f651b9c1f6a4c6c6eecd380\"> <img src=\"http://media.guim.co.uk/0a4fdce01e2d68712f651b9c1f6a4c6c6eecd380/0_0_318_469/318.jpg\" alt=\"Percy Jackson and the Lightning Thief\" width=\"318\" height=\"469\" class=\"gu-image\" /> </figure>  <p>A great book that blends Greek myths and the modern world together fantastically, with plenty of jokes and fun. Rick Riordan is an amazing author and this book is a must read for 8-10 year olds.</p> <ul> <li><strong>Buy this book at the <a href=\"https://bookshop.theguardian.com/percy-jackson-and-the-lightning-thief-3.html\">Guardian Bookshop</a></strong><br /></li> </ul> <h2><strong>Want to tell the world about a book you’ve read? <a href=\"http://www.theguardian.com/books/childrens-books/2011/mar/02/how-do-i-get-involved-guardian-childrens-books\">Join the site</a> and send us your review!</strong></h2>","productionOffice":"UK","trailText":"<strong>Smiley Carrot:</strong> ‘A great book that blends Greek myths and the modern world together fantastically, with plenty of jokes and fun’","headline":"Percy Jackson and the Lightning Thief by Rick Riordan - review","byline":"Smiley Carrott"},"webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/childrens-books-site/2016/mar/21/percy-jackson-and-the-lightning-thief-rick-riordan-review","apiUrl":"http://content.guardianapis.com/childrens-books-site/2016/mar/21/percy-jackson-and-the-lightning-thief-rick-riordan-review","sectionName":"Children's books","elements":[{"id":"0a4fdce01e2d68712f651b9c1f6a4c6c6eecd380","relation":"body","type":"image","assets":[{"type":"image","file":"http://media.guim.co.uk/0a4fdce01e2d68712f651b9c1f6a4c6c6eecd380/0_0_318_469/318.jpg","typeData":{"role":"thumbnail","mediaApiUri":"https://api.media.gutools.co.uk/images/0a4fdce01e2d68712f651b9c1f6a4c6c6eecd380","